projects.title: Marble Solitaire
projects.description: Puzzle game made for android. Made in Game Maker Studio 2. Available on google play store. Using Google Play Services API for cloud saving and online leaderboards

projects.title: Work Schedule
projects.description: A simple schedule made with javaScript, HTML & CSS. This page is for keeping track of your work-days/hours and has an basic total income calculation. The schedule is using javaScripts Date object.

projects.title: Fish Sim Game
projects.description: A little fish game testing out classes and game logic using states. The game is made with javascripts canvas and 2d context rendering

projects.title: Sundsvalls Spegeln
projects.description: Cinema site that contains movies, screenings, reviews and rating. Server is made using Express.js and implements REST API design, that fetches data from CMS API. The website is using serverside rendering (SSR), HTML is built and manipulated with the template engine pug.

Teaching music production and working as a personal assistant. When teaching I improved my social skills and the ability to plan, structure, and execute lessons. As a personal assistant I worked independently with a high responsability and handling of medicine.

Studying to become a fullstack developer in JavaScript and Java. From creating websites with HTML, CSS/SASS and JavaScript, testing with Jest and SuperTest, to designing REST-APIs with express.js. I have learned a variety of popular frameworks and libraries.
